source: cli/tests/help.rs
expression: text
---
Get or set the label of a btrfs filesystem

Usage: label <PATH> [NEW_LABEL]

Arguments:
  <PATH>
          The device or mount point to operate on

  [NEW_LABEL]
          The new label to set (if omitted, the current label is printed)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
